# shadcn MCP - UI Component Discovery

**When to use:**
- Building React Islands or UI components
- Need shadcn/ui component examples
- Finding component usage patterns
- Installing new shadcn components

**How to use:**
```typescript
// List available components
mcp_shadcn_list_items_in_registries({ registries: ["@shadcn"] })

// Search for components
mcp_shadcn_search_items_in_registries({
  registries: ["@shadcn"],
  query: "button"
})

// Get component details
mcp_shadcn_view_items_in_registries({
  items: ["@shadcn/button"]
})

// Get usage examples
mcp_shadcn_get_item_examples_from_registries({
  registries: ["@shadcn"],
  query: "button-demo"
})

// Get install command
mcp_shadcn_get_add_command_for_items({
  items: ["@shadcn/button"]
})
```

**Why:**
- Discover available components
- See real usage examples
- Get correct installation commands
- Find component patterns

**Use cases:**
- Building React Islands (`backend/static/src/components/islands/`)
- Adding shadcn components (`backend/static/src/components/ui/`)
- UI component development
